%TUTORIAL -------------------- EDIT - 'INFO' MACRO -------------------T
%OPTION  ===>_ZCMD

+The%INFO+macro is used to display information about the dataset current
 edited.  The infomation will be displayed as%NOTE+and%MSG+lines, which
 be processed by EDIT line commands, or deleted using the%RESET+command.
 event the NOTE and MSG lines will not be saved with the data.

 Information displayed by the INFO command:

  %o+Dataset name
  %o+Allocation information
  %o+Dataset attributes
  %o+Space statistics
  %o+Date flags
  %o+PDS Directory information (if available)
  %o+ISPF statistics (if available)
)PROC
 &ZUP = #EMCH
)END
